data.description: Newly refreshed one-level ranch located in a quiet, low traffic neighborhood. Two brand new bathrooms, kitchen with new Quartz counters, new luxury LVP flooring and new stainless sink. Southern view & natural light fills the family room and living room. Brand new mini-split heat pump system offers economical heat and A/C. Recently replaced roof and vinyl windows/doors. New interior and exterior paint. Low maintenance yard. Tranquil neighborhood yet near shopping, mall, freeway, restaurants, schools and park. No HOA.
